entries.npc_failure_1: Did I not tell you that this beast could not die? Why do you hunt what you can never catch? Why do you seek to go back to a time that is forever lost to you? Go, go away…
entries.npc_noloc_1: Soon, the beast shall make itself known soon…
entries.npc_work_1: Have you slain the monster, friend? Have you made the billions who stood by and watched this slaughter take place face their crime?
entries.npc_reward_1: The beast is defeated for now but it will return. It always returns…
entries.npc_backtowork_1: Yes, I also hear their voices. I see their pale faces staring at me. Accusing me. Please help me stop the monster that killed them.
entries.npc_4_1: I was there when the light was extinguished, friend. I helped extinguish it. Now I must live in darkness, for that is the only place that will have me. Will you help me stop this beast's rampage?
entries.npc_3_1: Who will shed light on the darkness? Who will restore order to the galaxy? I did not mean to kill the light...
entries.npc_2_1: Go quickly. Show no mercy. This foul thing corrupts everything it touches. It must be stopped. It can't be stopped. Go quickly.
entries.npc_1_1: He can't trick me. I know the Jedi were the guardians of peace and justice in the Old Republic. Everyone knew that. Yet no one did anything when they were hunted down. No one spoke out against the massacre. And now there is blood on my hands. This beast can never die, friend. But we must try nonetheless. Will you help me track this monster and stop its murderous rampage? We must act before the galaxy suffers. Before the darkness comes.
entries.npc_reset: The beast eventually drives everyone mad, friend. It will get you too. Run while you can.
entries.cantwork: My tasks are dangerous and require your full attention. Come back when you dare to face the savage beast.
entries.next: You've killed the beast for now, friend. But it always comes back. It always comes back…
